wing%20the%20announcement%20that%20the%20Fed%20held%20interest%20rates%20steady.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%20added%20that%20tariffs'%20effects%20on%20inflation%20could%20be%20either%20short-lived%20or%20more%20persistent%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20high%20they%20are%20and%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20for%20the%20effects%20to%20show%20up%20in%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariff-uncertainty-affecting-businesses-spending-prices-hiring-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETariff%20decisions%20have%20already%20affected%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20strategies%20and%20sales.%20Small-business%20owner%20Michael%20Salvatore%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20legal%20whiplash%20with%20tariffs%20means%20more%20uncertainty.%20While%20there%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bserious%20discussions%26quot%3B%20about%20increasing%20prices%20at%20his%20business%20locations%20in%20Chicago%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20only%20so%20much%20our%20customers%20can%20reasonably%20be%20expected%20to%20absorb%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20go%20back%20and%20forth%20on%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20small%20business%20owner%2C%20uncertainty%20is%20just%20as%20damaging%20as%20the%20tariffs%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Salvatore%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20make%20clear%20purchasing%20decisions%20or%20long-term%20plans%20when%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20rules%20I'm%20playing%20by.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHard%20economic%20data%20has%20stayed%20strong%2C%20including%20better-than-expected%20job%20growth%2C%20and%20even%20soft%20data%20is%20starting%20to%20improve.%20Changes%20to%20trade%20deals%20in%20May%2C%20such%20as%20the%2090-day%20pause%20on%20many%20tariffs%20with%20China%2C%20could%20be%20playing%20a%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Survey%20of%20Consumer%20Expectations%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20New%20York%20showed%20inflation%20expectations%20declined.%20New%20National%20Federation%20of%20Independent%20Business%20data%20showed%20small%20businesses%20were%20more%20optimistic%20in%20May%20after%20the%20index%20dropped%20the%20previous%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20optimism%20recovered%20slightly%20in%20May%2C%20uncertainty%20is%20still%20high%20among%20small%20business%20owners%2C%26quot%3B%20Bill%20Dunkelberg%2C%20NFIB's%20chief%20economist%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nfib.com%2Fnews%2Fpress-release%2Fnew-nfib-survey-small-business-optimism-increases-in-may%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20economy%20will%20continue%20to%20stumble%20along%20until%20the%20major%20sources%20of%20uncertainty%20are%20resolved%2C%20owners%20reported%20more%20positive%20expectations%20on%20business%20conditions%20and%20sales%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story.%20Please%20check%20back%20for%20updates.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-may-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749645119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684881cb85e81483682bd099%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-may-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20made%20new%20trade%20deals%20in%20May%2C%20tariff%20effects%20are%20showing%20up%20in%20the%20consumer%20price%20index%20data.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Madison%20Hoff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-may-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22