sword-health-cuts-physical-therapists-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%243%20billion%20musculoskeletal%20startup%20Sword%20Health%20started%20using%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20generate%20messages%20for%20physical%20therapists%20to%20send%20to%20patients%20last%20year%2C%20BI%20reported%20in%20November.%20%241.6%20billion%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ai-nurses-treat-patients-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHippocratic%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20taking%20it%20a%20step%20further%2C%20partnering%20with%20Nvidia%20to%20create%20generative%20AI%20%26quot%3Bnurses%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20video%20chat%20with%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuffy%20said%20creating%20a%20chatbot%20to%20message%20patients%20instead%20of%20a%20care%20team%20is%20%26quot%3Btoo%20easy.%26quot%3B%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20tools%20on%20the%20market%20are%20%26quot%3Bembellished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20getting%20the%20big%20box%20models%2C%20opening%20up%20their%20API%2C%20and%20having%20a%20support%20agent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20Omada's%20new%20AI%20agent%20for%20nutrition%20goal-setting%2C%20a%20practice%20backed%20by%20clinical%20evidence%2C%20and%20which%20on%20Omada's%20platform%20delivers%20discreet%20insights%20that%20help%20providers%20better%20care%20for%20patients.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20clear%20to%20members%20that%20they're%20messaging%20an%20AI%20agent%20rather%20than%20a%20provider%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAm%20I%20going%20to%20expect%20Omada's%20users%20to%20carve%20out%2010%20minutes%20on%20a%20Saturday%20to%20chat%20with%20a%20model%3F%20No.%20But%20our%20care%20teams%20can%20hold%20accountability%20against%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Duffy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22baa85fa8-9014-43b3-9dcf-cea253d9a915%5C%22%3EBucking%20the%20trends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EClinical%20evidence%20has%20long%20been%20Omada's%20north%20star%3B%20the%20company%20has%20published%2030%20peer-reviewed%20papers%20over%20the%20years%20about%20the%20efficacy%20of%20its%20various%20products.%20So%20it's%20perhaps%20no%20surprise%20that%20Omada%20hasn't%20rushed%20to%20apply%20AI%20to%20its%20platform%20without%20clinical%20evidence%20to%20support%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Justin%20Wu%2C%20Omada%20Health's%20vice%20president%20of%20clinical%20innovation%20and%20quality%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20May%20that%20the%20company%20finally%20feels%20ready%20to%20allow%20patients%20to%20interact%20with%20AI%20directly%20after%20significant%20improvements%20in%20the%20underlying%20models.%20He%20added%20that%20Omada%20fine-tuned%20its%20new%20AI%20agent%20with%20its%20own%20clinical%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20similarly%20refused%20to%20hop%20on%20the%20GLP-1%20bandwagon%20as%20new%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%20take%20over%20the%20market.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-ozempic-leading-ipo-omada-health-latest-growth-surge-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOmada's%20metabolic%20care%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20taken%20off%2C%20including%20to%20manage%20patients%20taking%20GLP-1%20drugs%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomada-strategy-weight-loss-drugs-semaglutide-ozempic-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edoesn't%20prescribe%20the%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20unlike%20many%20of%20its%20public%20and%20private%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuffy%20clarified%20that%20Omada%20hasn't%20shied%20away%20from%20prescribing%20GLP-1s%20because%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20do%20so.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20remind%20people%20that%20we%20prescribe%20%5Bcontinuous%20glucose%20monitors%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPrescribing%20is%20not%20that%20hard%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20says%20Omada%20prefers%20to%20allow%20patients'%20primary%20care%20doctors%20to%20prescribe%20the%20medications.%20Omada's%20job%20is%20to%20augment%20primary%20care%2C%20not%20replace%20it%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20the%20company%20won't%20be%20swayed%20if%20its%20members%20consistently%20want%20to%20get%20their%20GLP-1%20prescriptions%20from%20Omada%2C%20Duffy%20said.%20He%20said%20he%20hasn't%20seen%20that%20demand%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20let%20the%20members%20speak%2C%20so%20if%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2010%20out%20of%2010%20members%20next%20year%20are%20like%2C%20please%2C%20Omada%2C%20help%20me%20here%2C%20we%20may%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20our%20strategy%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmada%20went%20public%20on%20June%206th%20at%20a%20%241.1%20billion%20valuation%2C%20similar%20to%20its%20last%20public%20market%20valuation%20of%20over%20%241%20billion%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20%24192%20million%20Series%20E%20in%202022.%20Its%20stock%20opened%20at%20%2423%20a%20share%2C%2021%25%20above%20its%20initial%20price.%20It%20was%20trading%20at%20%2422.60%20at%20Monday's%20close.%20CAN%20WE%20UPDATE%20THIS%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomada-health-resisting-ai-push-after-ipo-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749643201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684756ae85e81483682bbecb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomada-health-resisting-ai-push-after-ipo-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Newly%20public%20Omada%20Health%20says%20it%20won't%20turn%20patient%20care%20over%20to%20AI%20as%20the%20tech%20consumes%20investor%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rtorrence%40businessinsider.com%20(Rebecca%20Torrence)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomada-health-resisting-ai-push-after-ipo-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%