2Fi.insider.com%2F610118350d35a90018258a41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22645%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20trader%20rubs%20his%20eyes%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBond%20giant%20Pimco%20warns%20that%20equity%20valuations%20are%20historically%20high.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20current%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20CAPE%20ratio%20is%20in%20the%2094th%20percentile%20of%20all-time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEquity%20risk%20premium%20is%20also%20around%20as%20low%20as%20it%20was%20before%20the%201987%20crash%20and%20the%20dot-com%20bust.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20tranquil%20few%20weeks%20for%20financial%20markets%20as%20investors%20wait%20to%20see%20how%20the%20US%20economy%20holds%20up%20under%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20tariff%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20could%20change%20quickly%2C%20Pimco%20warned%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20several%20measures%2C%20stock%20valuations%20are%20sitting%20at%20levels%20historically%20seen%20before%20big%20corrections%2C%20the%20%242%20trillion%20asset%20manager%20said%20in%20a%20note%20written%20by%20global%20economic%20advisor%20Richard%20Clarida%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20Fixed%20Income%20Andrew%20Balls%2C%20and%20group%20chief%20investment%20officer%20Dan%20Ivascyn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20gauge%20they%20cited%20is%20the%20Shiller%20cyclically-adjusted%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%2C%20which%20compares%20the%20current%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20price%20to%20a%2010-year%20moving%20average%20of%20its%20earnings.%20Its%20current%20level%20of%20around%2036x%20earnings%20is%20in%20the%20all-time%2094th%20percentile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22shiller%20pe%20ratio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68488fa085e81483682bd34d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22380%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPIMCO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20measure%20is%20the%20equity%20risk%20premium%2C%20or%20the%20projected%20assumed%20returns%20of%20stocks%20over%2010-year%20Treasurys%20based%20on%20current%20valuations.%20Sitting%20near%20zero%2C%20the%20ERP%20has%20only%20been%20this%20low%2010%25%20of%20the%20time.%20When%20it's%20been%20this%20low%20in%20the%20past%2C%20significant%20stock-market%20declines%20have%20followed%20%E2%80%94%20see%20the%201987%20crash%20and%20the%20dot-com%20bust%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222168%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22us%20equity%20risk%20premium%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68488fbb3d5881a51c1b2558%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22774%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPIMCO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20mean%20reversion%20to%20a%20higher%20equity%20risk%20premium%20typically%20involves%20a%20bond%20rally%2C%20an%20equity%20sell-off%2C%20or%20both%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20same%20chart%20shows%20two%20prior%20times%20when%20the%20premium%20was%20zero%20or%20negative%3A%20in%201987%20and%20in%201996%E2%80%942001.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20zero%20equity%20risk%20premium%20in%20September%201987%2C%20the%20stock%20market%20declined%20by%20almost%2025%25%2C%20while%2030-year%20real%20bond%20yields%20fell%20by%2080%20basis%20points%20(bps).%20In%20December%201999%2C%20the%20equity%20risk%20premium%20reached%20its%20minimum%20level%20during%20the%20chart%20period%2C%20preceding%20an%20equity%20drawdown%20of%20almost%2040%25%20that%20ended%20in%20February%202003.%20In%20that%20same%20time%2C%2030-year%20real%20bond%20yields%20fell%20by%20about%20200%20bps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh%20stock%20valuations%20make%20it%20likely%20that%20fixed-income%20assets%20outperform%20stocks%20in%20the%20years%20ahead%2C%20the%2