in%202018.%20It%20currently%20holds%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fworld-records%2F589898-most-visited-museum-single-art-group%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGuinness%20World%20Record%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20most-visited%20museum%20dedicated%20to%20a%20single%20group%20or%20artist%2C%20bringing%20in%20more%20than%202.5%20million%20visitors%20from%20April%202023%20to%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20popular%20second%20location%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20known%20as%20teamLab%20Borderless%2C%20focuses%20on%20digital%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20museums%20were%20launched%20by%20teamLab%2C%20an%20international%20art%20collective%20that%20includes%20artists%2C%20animators%2C%20engineers%2C%20mathematicians%2C%20and%20architects%20among%20its%20specialists.%20Together%2C%20they%20work%20to%20%26quot%3Bexplore%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20self%20and%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20museum's%20website%2C%20although%20global%20brand%20director%20Takashi%20Kudo%20said%20they%20have%20an%20even%20bigger%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20these%20exhibitions%20cannot%20reach%20an%20emotional%20height%2C%20then%20we%20have%20failed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F12%2F07%2Farts%2Fdesign%2Fteamlab-tokyo-abu-dhabi-digital-art.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20reach%20people's%20hearts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEven%20during%20the%20peak%20season%20in%20March%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20easily%20book%20tickets.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20exhibit%20at%20teamLab%20Planets%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6843255185e81483682b9cd2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20immersive%20digital%20exhibit%20at%20teamLab%20Planets%20in%20Tokyo.%3Cp%3EPHILIP%20FONG%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETeamLab%20Planets%20offers%20time%20slots%20from%209%20a.m.%20to%208%3A30%20p.m.%20Just%20about%20every%20travel%20blog%20recommends%20visiting%20the%20museum%20when%20it%20opens%20to%20beat%20crowds%20(and%20have%20fewer%20people%20in%20your%20Instagram%20shots)%2C%20which%20means%20every%20morning%20slot%20was%20sold%20out%20when%20I%20tried%20to%20book%20tickets%20about%20a%20week%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20figured%20the%20nighttime%20slots%20might%20be%20less%20crowded%2C%20so%20I%20booked%20two%20tickets%20for%207%3A30%20p.m.%20The%20total%20was%208%2C800%20yen%2C%20or%20about%20%2461.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20visiting%2C%20we%20found%20some%20helpful%20tips%20online%20for%20what%20to%20wear.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20exhibit%20at%20teamLab%20Planets%20in%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6843244c85e81483682b9c97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETeamLab%20Planets%20recommends%20wearing%20shorts%20or%20pants%20that%20easily%20roll%20up%20for%20its%20exhibits.%3Cp%3EKazuhiro%20NOGI%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20travel%20blogs%20and%20our%20friends'%20Google%20Docs%20noted%20that%20part%20of%20the%20museum's%20experience%20involves%20walking%20through%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20made%20sure%20to%20wear%20shoes%20that%20could%20quickly%20slip%20off%20and%20pants%20that%20could%20easily%20roll%20up.%20Since%20the%20floors%20are%20mirrored%2C%20a%20number%20of%20blogs%20recommended%20skipping%20skirts%20or%20short%20dresses.%20Shorts%20are%20also%20available%20to%20rent%20for%20free%20if%20you%20need%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20arrived%2030%20minutes%20before%20our%20time%20slot%20began%2C%20and%20found%20a%20line%20already%20curving%20around%20the%20building.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20reflection%20in%20the%20rainbow%20room%20of%20TeamLab%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fdbbf33fe8d39283630e6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BInfinite%20Crystal%20Universe%26quot%3B%20exhibit%20at%20teamLab%20Planets.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20quickly%20made%20it%20past%20the%20gates%20of%20the%2010%2C000-square-foot%20warehouse%2C%20where%20we%20were%20welcomed%20with%20a%20towering%20sculpture%20called%20%26quot%3BUniverse%20of%20Fire%20Particles%20Haunting%20the%20Sky%20and%20Earth.%26quot%3B%20The%20lit-up%20piece%2C%20glowing%20with%20red%20and%20yellow%20flames%2C%20changes%20as%20people%20stand%20near%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20art%20can%20be%20found%20at%20Vegan%20Ramen%20UZU%2C%20the%20museum's%20ramen%20shop.%20I%20wish%20I%20hadn't%20grabbed%20dinner%20beforehand%20because%20a%20friend%20later%20told%20me%20this%20was%20one%20of%20her%20favorite%20ramen%20experiences%20in%20all%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-us-to-tokyo-japan-better-quality-of-life-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETokyo%3C%2Fa%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20watching%20a%20quick%20introductory%20video%2C%20our%20experience%20at%20teamLab%20Planets%20began.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20water%20exhibits%20at%20teamLab%20Planets%20in%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684323b8f748d8c055f335ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20water%20exhibits%20at%20teamLab%20Planets%20in%20Tokyo.%3Cp%3EPHILIP%20FONG%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20sections%3A%20Water%2C%20Athletics%20Forest%2C%20and%20Garden.%20The%20forest%20section%2C%20which%20opened%20in%20January%2C%20had%20added%2020%20new%20exhibits%20to%20the%20original%20nine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20left%20our%20bags%20and%20shoes%20in%20the%20free%20lockers%2C%20which%20came%20with%20keys%20we%20could%20wear%20as%20bracelets.%20Then%2C%20we%20walked%20up%20a%20ramp%20as%20we%20headed%20into%20the%20water%20exhibit%2C%20our%20feet%20softly%20splashing%20beneath%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first%20major%20exhibit%20was%20the%20famous%20%26quot%3BInfinite%20Crystal%20Universe.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20room%20full%20of%20sparkles%20at%20TeamLab%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fdbbd3c6ad288d147e2481%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlthough%20I%20had%20seen%20it%20plenty%20of%20times%20on%20Instagram%2C%20I%20still%20loved%20walking%20through%20the%20%26quot%3BInfinite%20Crystal%20Universe%26quot%3B%20exhibit.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20walking%20through%20nearly%20pitch-black%20spaces%2C%20the%20world%20opens%20to%20a%20dazzling%20room%20filled%20with%20hundreds%20of%20shimmering%20LED%20lights.%20They%20seemed%20to%20go%20on%20forever%2C%20a%20trick%20of%20the%20eye%20achieved%20by%20the%20mirrored%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20it's%20because%20I'm%20partial%20to%20sparkle%20eyeshadow%20and%20the%20exhibit%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20makeup%20bag%2C%20but%20how%20could%20you%20not%20love%20pretty%20lights%3F%20I%20was%20entranced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20all%20the%20exhibits%20at%20teamLab%20Planets%2C%20the%20lights%20are%20affected%20by%20the%20presence%20of%20those%20around%20them.%20Attendees%20who%20download%20the%20teamLab%20Planets%20app%20can%20even%20choose%20which%20colors%20light%20up.%20It%20allows%20the%20piece%20to%20evolve%20constantly%2C%20ensuring%20it's%20never%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENext%20up%20was%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20exhibits%2C%20the%20glowing%20koi%20pond.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20room%20full%20of%20glowing%20fish%20in%20water%20at%20TeamLab%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fdbc0f3fe8d39283630e6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWatching%20the%20rainbow%20koi%20fish%20swim%20through%20the%20water.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20walked%20into%20the%20dark%20room%20as%20a%20rainbow%20of%20digital%20koi%20fish%20swam%20in%20the%20warm%20water%20around%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20time%20a%20koi%20fish%20collided%20with%20our%20leg%2C%20it%20transformed%20into%20a%20lovely%20flower.%20According%20to%20the%20museum's%20website%2C%20these%20flowers%20change%20depending%20on%20what%20season%20you%20visit%20the%20exhibit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%2C%20we%20walked%20into%20a%20room%20filled%20with%20ginormous%20balloons.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20balloon%20room%20at%20TeamLab%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fdbc233fe8d39283630e6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20room%20full%20of%20massive%20glowing%20spheres%20was%20a%20blast.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20boyfriend%20and%20I%20giggled%20like%20kids%20as%20we%20wandered%20through%20the%20massive%20spheres%2C%20which%20changed%20color%20whenever%20we%20touched%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20room%20glowed%20bright%20pink%2C%20blue%2C%20and%20green%20as%20we%20bounced%20and%20pushed%20the%20spheres%20around%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20room%20called%20%26quot%3BFloating%20in%20