ect%20moment%2C%20as%20I%20fully%20immersed%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20bounced%20on%20the%20rotating%20spheres%20and%20balanced%20on%20stepping%20stones%2C%20I%20felt%20transported%20back%20to%20the%20games%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20used%20to%20make%20up%20on%20the%20playground%2C%20when%20the%20only%20available%20entertainment%20was%20our%20imagination%20and%20some%20monkey%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%26quot%3BGraffiti%20Nature%26quot%3B%20was%20another%20favorite%20exhibit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drawing%20projections%20at%20TeamLab%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fdbc3dc6ad288d147e2489%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20wall%20full%20of%20everyone's%20drawings%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BGraffiti%20Nature%26quot%3B%20exhibit.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20boyfriend%20and%20I%20were%20happy%20to%20stumble%20on%20a%20table%20full%20of%20people%20coloring%20pictures%20of%20flowers%2C%20butterflies%2C%20snakes%2C%20and%20lizards.%20A%20full%20day%20of%20sightseeing%20was%20quickly%20catching%20up%20to%20us%2C%20and%20we%20needed%20a%20sedentary%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20finished%20coloring%2C%20a%20teamLab%20staff%20member%20took%20our%20drawings%20and%20put%20them%20through%20a%20special%20printer.%20Suddenly%2C%20our%20illustrations%20were%20projected%20across%20the%20entire%20room.%20My%20boyfriend's%20snake%20slithered%20by%20our%20feet%20as%20my%20flower%20multiplied%20on%20the%20walls.%20It%20was%20a%20total%20surprise%20and%20a%20moment%20of%20pure%20delight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELast%20but%20not%20least%20was%20the%20famous%20floating%20flower%20garden.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anneta%20in%20the%20floating%20flower%20garden%20at%20TeamLab%20Tokyo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%2