g%20more%20prepared%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20round%20was%20a%20human%20interview%2C%20but%20I%20chose%20not%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20the%20company%20for%20other%20reasons.%20I'm%20still%20interviewing%20for%20jobs%2C%20and%20I've%20used%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-coach-shares-5-tips-acing-ai-interviews-tests-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einsights%20from%20my%20AI%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20more%20conscious%20of%20the%20aspects%20it%20ranked%20me%20positively%20and%20negatively%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20this%20experience%2C%20if%20I%20were%20to%20do%20another%20AI%20interview%2C%20I%20would%20focus%20on%20being%20more%20prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20humans%20generally%20involve%20some%20level%20of%20subjectivity%20in%20their%20assessment%20of%20someone%2C%20AI%20is%20objective.%20It%20has%20a%20clear%20set%20of%20parameters%20on%20which%20it%20evaluates%20you%2C%20so%20you%20need%20to%20be%20prepared%20to%20confidently%20and%20clearly%20share%20your%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20is%20not%20to%20underestimate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hiring-tools-biased-as-humans-experts-warn-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI%20interview%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20be%20prepared%2C%20be%20real%2C%20and%2C%20per%20my%20experience%2C%20dress%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20unique%20job%20interview%20experience%20that%20you%20would%20like%20to%20share%2C%20please%20email%20the%20editor%2C%20Manseen%20Logan%2C%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amlogan%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emlogan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterviewed-by-ai-bot-for-tech-job-pros-cons-tips-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%