le%20the%20stress%3A%20Lego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-consultancies-leaders-pwc-deloitte-ey-kpmg-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBig%20Four%3C%2Fa%3E%20professional%20services%20firm%20has%20updated%20its%20long-running%20well-being%20subsidy%20program%20to%20include%20%26quot%3BLegos%20and%20puzzles%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20list%20of%20items%20that%20Deloitte%20will%20reimburse%2C%20internal%20policy%20documents%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20has%20long%20offered%20eligible%20US%20staff%20an%20annual%20subsidy%20to%20spend%20on%20one%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20subscriptions%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%20experiences.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20firm%20doubled%20the%20allowance%20from%20%24500%20to%20%241%2C000%2C%20an%20internal%20webpage%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20subsidy%20is%20meant%20to%20%26quot%3Bempower%20and%20support%20your%20journey%20toward%20thriving%20mentally%2C%20physically%2C%20and%20financially%20and%20living%20your%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20policy%20documents%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20partners%20and%20salaried%20workers%20are%20offered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployee-wellbeing-programs-help-companies-perform-better-and-manage-cost-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20benefit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Interns%2C%20contracted%20professionals%2C%20and%20employees%20on%20a%20leave%20of%20absence%20are%20not%20eligible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Deloitte%20US%20employee%20told%20BI%20that%20people%20were%20discussing%20the%20new%20updates%20in%20internal%20team%20chats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20responses%20are%20things%20like%20'Lego%3F!%3F!%3F%20Finally!'%20or%20jokes%20about%20how%20they%20can%20now%20rationalize%20buying%20the%20coveted%20Millennium%20Falcon%20Star%20Wars%20Lego%20set%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELego's%20most%20expensive%20set%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20hr