f%20Deloitte's%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%20section%20titled%20%26quot%3Bwhat's%20new%20for%20FY26%26quot%3B%20are%20kitchenware%20and%20kitchen%20appliances%20(e.g.%2C%20blender%2C%20refrigerator)%2C%20spa%20services%20like%20facials%20and%20body%20treatments%2C%20personal%20portable%20cooling%20fans%2C%20and%20ergonomic%2C%20cooling%2C%20and%20sleeping%20pillows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20can%20also%20spend%20the%20subsidy%20on%20items%20like%20office%20furniture%2C%20gym%20equipment%2C%20financial%20support%20apps%2C%20fitness%20classes%2C%20and%20gaming%20consoles%2C%20including%20the%20Nintendo%20Switch%20and%20PlayStation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeloitte%20US%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20are%20as%20positive%20about%20the%20subsidy%20program%2C%20with%20one%20Deloitte%20US%20employee%20telling%20BI%20they%20think%20it%20is%20only%20given%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20of%20how%20much%20this%20job%20sucks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20division%20of%20Deloitte%20has%20faced%20a%20challenging%20period%20after%20its%20contracts%20with%20the%20government%20came%20under%20scrutiny%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%20Office's%3C%2Fa%3E%20efforts%20to%20cut%20federal%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20April%2C%20at%20least%20127%20of%20the%20firm's%20government%20contracts%20had%20been%20cut%20or%20modified%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-doge-consulting-crackdown-contracts-cuts-big-four-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBI's%20analysis%20of%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20DOGE%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20month%2C%20Deloitte%20Consulting%20CEO%20Jason%20Salzetti%20said%20in%20an%20internal%20meeting%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20percentage%26quot%3B%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20firm's%20g