heir%20grill%20scrubber.%3Cp%3EJJGeorge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDestin%20Sandlin%2C%20creator%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BSmarter%20Every%20Day%26quot%3B%20series%20on%20YouTube%2C%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20better%20grill%20scrubber.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20wanted%20to%20build%20the%20product%20entirely%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20spent%20four%20years%20working%20on%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESandlin%20documented%20the%20process%20in%20a%20video.%20The%20first%20batch%20of%20the%20%2475%20scrubbers%20sold%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20really%20nice%20grill%20brush%20will%20cost%20you%20about%20%2425%20at%20your%20local%20big%20box%20store%2C%20but%20YouTuber%20Dustin%20Sandlin%20is%20betting%20he%20can%20get%20customers%20to%20shell%20out%20three%20times%20that%20amount%20for%20a%20Made-in-America%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESandlin%20traces%20his%20passion%20for%20US%20manufacturing%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20in%202020%2C%20when%20he%20was%20bothered%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20American-made%20essential%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20wanted%20N95%20masks%20and%20face%20shields%2C%20and%20they%20couldn't%20get%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20YouTube%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3ZTGwcHQfLY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThis%20revealed%20to%20me%20how%20anemic%20our%20manufacturing%20capacity%20in%20America%20has%20become%2C%20because%20I%20was%20waiting%20on%20some%20billionaire%20to%20come%20save%20us%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20began%20a%20yearslong%20deep%20dive%20into%20the%20challenges%20of%20making%20products%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20Sandlin%20documented%20for%20his%20series%20on%20YouTube%20called%20%26quot%3BSmarter%20Every%20Day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20with%20John%20Youngblood%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20local%20specialty%20grill%20accessories%20company%2C%20Sandlin%20got%20excited%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20developing%20a%20better%20scrubber.%20Sandlin%20and%20Youngblood%20wanted%20to%20produce%20it%20in%20the%20US%20with%20as%20many%20domestically%20sourced%20components%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafina-shower-head-founder-tests-paying-more-american-made-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esell%20it%20at%20a%20retail%20price%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3ZTGwcHQfLY%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22I%20Tried%20To%20Make%20Something%20In%20America%20(The%20Smarter%20Scrubber%20Experiment)%20-%20Smarter%20Every%20Day%20308%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20that%20went%20live%20Sunday%20and%20has%20since%20amassed%20more%20than%202%20million%20views%2C%20Sandlin%20shares%20why%20he%20decided%20to%20get%20serious%20about%20US%20manufacturing%2C%20explains%20how%20he%20navigated%20the%20design%20process%2C%20and%20makes%20a%20sales%20pitch%20for%20viewers%20to%20buy%20it%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Youngblood%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20%2475%20scrubber%20has%20sold%20through%20its%20initial%20production%20run%20of%20several%20thousand%20units%20within%20a%20day%2C%20and%20his%20company%20is%20now%20taking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jjgeorgestore.com%2Fthe-smarter-scrubber%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epre-orders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20backlog%20for%20a%20while%2C%26quot%3B%20Youngblood%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb7b813a-5836-40fb-b162-eafaa972768f%5C%22%3EMost%20grill%20brushes%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20thrown%20away.%20This%20one%20isn't.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20lower-cost%20grill%20brushes%20aren't%20typically%20designed%20to%20last%20more%20than%20a%20year%20of%20use%20%E2%80%94%20grill-maker%20Weber%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D37080671b052f23e3693df98b5f739de71b1e1989f30caaddd34c60100725701%26postID%3D6848650efd5275b1dedbb669%26postSlug%3Dyoutuber-destin-sandlin-created-grill-scrubber-challenge-manufacturing-in-us-2025-6%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.weber.com%252FUS%252Fen%252Fblog%252Ftips-techniques%252Fgrill-brush-care%252Fweber-31092.html%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecommends%3C%2Fa%3E%20changing%20them%20after%20each%20grilling%20season.%20Another%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20bristles%20have%20been%20known%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumerreports.org%2Ffood-safety%2Fwire-grill-brush-danger%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecome%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20can%20end%20up%20in%20grilled%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESandlin%20and%20Youngblood%20found%20that%20welded%20chain%20mail%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20material%20of%20a%20medieval%20knight's%20armor%20%E2%80%94%20was%20highly%20effective%20at%20cleaning%20grill%20grates%20without%20breaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20one%20problem%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%20only%20find%20it%20in%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20tries%2C%20the%20team%20managed%20to%20find%20a%20US%20supplier%20who%20could%20make%20about%202%2C000%20units%20a%20month%20and%20a%20supplier%20in%20India%20to%20augment%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttaching%20the%20chain%20mail%20to%20a%20handle%20proved%20to%20be%20another%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESandlin%20said%20the%20average%20one-inch%20industrial%20bolt%20costs%20around%209%20cents%20when%20imported%2C%20but%20that%20jumps%20to%2038%20cents%20for%20versions%20made%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20machine%20shops%20I%20talked%20to%20directly%2C%20they%20said%2C%20'Yeah%2C%20we%20can't%20even%20get%20the%20material%20for%20the%20price%20of%20the%20finished%20bolts%20that%20you're%20getting%20from%20a%20foreign%20supplier%2C'%26quot%3B%20Sandlin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20was%20the%20process%20of%20making%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcirkul-ceo-making-product-in-us-helped-speed-up-growth-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einjection-molded%20parts%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20provide%20support%20and%20flexibility%2C%20which%20required%20machining%20custom%20tools%20and%20dies%20(the%20metal%20forms%20that%20shape%20a%20material)%20for%20shops%20to%20use%20in%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20moment%20where%20this%20whole%20experiment%20came%20into%20focus%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandlin%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20realized%20at%20that%20moment%20we're%20screwed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220758d99c-2241-4005-b2d6-4a5cf36fcee3%5C%22%3EAmerican%20manufacturing%20has%20exported%20the%20smart%20part%20of%20making%20stuff%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20Sandlin's%20pessimism%20is%20that%20many%20of%20the%20shops%20he%20spoke%20with%20send%20tool%20and%20die%20design%20files%20to%20China%20to%20be%20made%20and%20imported%20for%20use%20in%20US%20production%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20my%20intellectual%20property%20in%20China%2C%20I%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-made-in-usa-american-brands-domestic-manufacturing-benefits-challenges-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emake%20it%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they%20said%2C%20'Good%20luck.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20illuminated%20by%20this%20episode%20goes%20far%20beyond%20a%20seemingly%20simple%20grilling%20accessory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20screwed%20as%20a%20