Kachi%20Haldi%20ki%20Sabji%2C%20Kuga%20Roti%2C%20and%20Makhaniya%20Lassi%2C%20winning%20hearts%20(and%20taste%20buds)%20from%20judges%20and%20chefs%20from%20across%20the%20world.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20formal%20training%2C%20but%20I%20had%20the%20flavours%20of%20my%20culture%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20was%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELaunching%20%E2%80%98Sidhi%20Marwari%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20brand%20born%20of%20belief%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20MasterChef%2C%20Kaushalya%20realised%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F411753%2Fmadhuras-recipe-maharashtrian-cuisine-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20having%20her%20platform%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20just%20a%20social%20media%20page%2C%20but%20something%20she%20could%20build%20on%20her%20terms.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20TikTok%20was%20banned%20in%20India%2C%20I%20lost%2015%20lakh%20subscribers%20and%20the%20revenue%20that%20was%20generated%20out%20of%20the%20videos%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kaushalya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20my%20earning%20resource%20is%20via%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20YouTube%2C%20Instagram%20or%20Facebook.%20If%20the%20platform%20is%20no%20longer%20there%2C%20what%20will%20I%20do%20for%20money%3F%E2%80%9D%20Kaushalya%20asked%20herself.%20This%20gave%20birth%20to%20%E2%80%98Sidhi%20Marwari%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20brand%20rooted%20in%20purity%20and%20tradition%20in%20March%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20came%20from%20a%20simple%20problem%3A%20her%20relatives%20abroad%20often%20complained%20that%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20the%20same%20flavour%20in%20Indian%20food%20made%20with%20foreign%20spices%20and%20oils.%20She%20visited%20factories%20and%20found%20poor%20hygiene%2C%20artificial%20colours%2C%20and%20shortcuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_VQEkUSsvz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_VQEkUSsvz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_VQEkUSsvz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Kaushalya%20Choudhary%20(%40kaushalyaair)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%2C%20why%20not%20make%20what%20our%20grandmothers%20used%20to%3F%20Pure%20spices.%20Cold-pressed%20oils.%20No%20preservatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20setup%20is%20delightfully%20old-school%20yet%20ingenious.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20%3Cem%3Egathiyas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bundles%20of%20spices)%20just%20like%20our%20grandmothers%20did%20%E2%80%94%20by%20hand.%20We%20attach%20them%20to%20motors%20that%20rotate%20at%20the%20same%20speed%20as%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20hand.%20That%20way%2C%20the%20flavour%20stays%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20batch%20sold%20out.%20Orders%20for%20five%20to%2010%20kg%20started%20pouring%20in.%20Today%2C%20Sidhi%20Marwari%20has%2015%20outlets%20across%20India%20and%20ships%20