in-law%20and%20her%20uncle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20business%20was%20started%20in%202024%2C%20she%20has%20been%20struggling%20for%20four%20years%20to%20build%20an%20app%20and%20a%20website%20as%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20took%20money%20from%20us%2C%20but%20did%20not%20provide%20the%20output%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Virendra%2C%20as%20someone%20who%20has%20seen%20her%20hardships%20first-hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20business%20built%20by%20women%2C%20for%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20Kaushalya%E2%80%99s%20journey%20even%20more%20inspiring%20is%20who%20she%E2%80%99s%20brought%20along%20with%20her.%20Her%20factory%20in%20rural%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20is%20managed%20by%20her%20father-in-law%20and%20her%20uncle%2C%20now%20employs%20over%2035%20women%20from%20nearby%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20clear.%20The%20women%20in%20our%20villages%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20leave%20home%20for%20jobs.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20create%20employment%20right%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20She%20now%20mentors%20other%20women%20to%20become%20financially%20independent.%20%E2%80%9CI%20tell%20them%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20wait%20for%20time.%20Make%20time.%20Even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20one%20hour%20a%20day%2C%20use%20it%20to%20work%20on%20your%20dream.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStaying%20grounded%2C%20dreaming%20bigger%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20the%20fame%20and%20success%2C%20Kaushalya%20remains%20grounded.%20%E2%80%9CI%20still%20want%20to%20be%20the%20same%20daughter-in-law%2C%20mother%2C%20and%20sister%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been.%20I%20just%20want%20more%20women%20to%20realise%20their%20worth%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20goal%20now%3F%20To%20help%20thousands%20of%20Kaushalyas%20rise%20from%20small%20villages%2C%20not%20just%20to%20seek%20jobs%2C%20but%20to%20build%20empires%20of%20their%20own.%20She%E2%80%