the%20health%20hazards%20associated%20with%20modern%20concrete%20and%20its%20finishes.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20cement%20concrete%2C%20follows%20plaster%20and%20heavy%2C%20toxic%20paints%20on%20top%20of%20these%20layers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrithika%20also%20worked%20on%20a%20study%20along%20with%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Madras%20in%202020%20to%20measure%20the%20indoor%20air%20quality%20index%20for%20Chennai%20households.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20found%20that%20apartments%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20VOCs%20(Volatile%20Organic%20Compounds).%20We%20found%20the%20air%20quality%20index%20was%20so%20bad%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20outdoors%2C%20contributing%20to%20%E2%80%98sick%20building%20syndrome%E2%80%99%20as%20recognised%20by%20the%20WHO%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreathing%20walls%20and%20earthy%20floors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20the%20antidote%3F%20For%20Krithika%20and%20her%20team%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20return%20to%20the%20wisdom%20of%20traditional%20building%20practices%2C%20using%20materials%20that%20are%20kind%20to%20the%20earth%20and%20to%20the%20people%20who%20inhabit%20the%20structures.%20Her%20approach%20to%20building%20emphasises%20the%20use%20of%20natural%20and%20locally%20sourced%20materials%20and%20we%20have%20broken%20it%20down%20for%20you.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20was%20such%20that%20not%20only%20did%20it%20give%20people%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F419684%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-using-stone-lime-moss-the-timber-residence-vagator%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthier%20option%20to%20live%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebut%20also%20the%20force%20that%20was%20working%20with%20these%20natural%20materials%20saw%20a%20betterment%20in%20their%20health.%20%E2%80%9CA%20few%20of%20my%20painters%20who%20do%20lime%20wash%20and%20lime%20plastic%20have%20told%20me%20that%20since%20they%20started%20working%20with%20natural%20substances%2C%20they%20did%20not%20encounter%20a%20problem%20of%20sinus%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhanajayan%20(52)%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20mason%20since%20he%20was%2015%20years%20old%2C%20shares%20that%20he%20enjoys%20working%20for%20sustainable%20buildings.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20interested%20in%20lime%20buildings%20since%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20involved%20in%20constructing%20buildings%20using%20traditional%20and%20old%20methods%20that%20eliminate%20concrete%20or%20cement%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHappy%20clients%2C%20happy%20planet%3A%20A%20win-win%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWord%20of%20Krithika%E2%80%99s%20unique%20approach%20has%20spread%2C%20and%20her%20clients%20are%20enamoured%20with%20the%20results.%20%E2%80%9CSlowly%2C%20by%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%20I%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20projects%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Krithika.%20They%20appreciate%20not%20just%20the%20aesthetic%20charm%20and%20the%20connection%20to%20nature%2C%20but%20also%20the%20holistic%20approach%20that%20considers%20everything%20from%20water%20management%20to%20the%20very%20air%20they%20breathe%20indoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20Subramanian%2C%20a%20satisfied%20client%20of%20Studio%20for%20Earthen%20Architecture%2C%20shares%20his%20experience%20of%20constructing%20an%20eco-friendly%20home%2035%20km%20away%20from%20Tirupathi%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20got%20to%20know%20about%20Krithika%E2%80%99s%20firm%20in%202020%2C%20they%20were%20relatively%20new%20to%20sustainable%20architecture%2C%20but%20I%20took%20this%20up%20as%20an%20experiment%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Krishna%2C%20who%20was%20passionate%20about%20constructing%20an%20eco-friendly%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20initial%20outlay%20might%20be%20slightly%20higher%20due%20to%20the%20skilled%20craftsmanship%20involved%2C%20Krithika%20is%20clear%20about%20where%20the%20money%20goes.%20%E2%80%9CAround%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20construction%20cost%20goes%20directly%20to%20the%20artisans.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20about%20extracting%20resources%20to%20build%20a%20structure%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20investing%20in%20people%20so%20they%20can%20build%20better%2C%20more%20meaningful%20spaces%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20This%20focus%20on%20fair%20wages%20and%20valuing%20traditional%20skills%20resonates%20deeply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160736.527-1749206279.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20foyer%20of%20the%20house%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160736.527-1749206279.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160736.527-1749206279-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160736.527-1749206279-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160736.527-1749206279-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T160736.527-1749206279-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-445353%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKrithika%20believes%20in%20using%20elements%20that%20will%20suit%20the%20construction%20environment.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20compare%20with%20concrete%20buildings%2C%20lime%20buildings%20are%20both%20labour-intensive%20and%2015%20percent%20higher%20in%20cost.%20If%2050%20kg%20of%20cement%20costs%20around%20Rs%20400%2C%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20lime%20would%20cost%20Rs%20600%20to%20700%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dhanajayan%2C%20explaining%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Krishna%20agrees%20with%20the%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20he%20spent%20more%20than%2040%20percent%20of%20what%20he%20had%20allocated%20%E2%80%94%20he%20is%20also%20happy%20that%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F312182%2Fmaking-of-odisha-krushi-bhavan-sustainable-architecture-local-craftsmanship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskill%20transfer%20for%20the%20artisans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20labour-intensive%20job%2C%20we%20need%20to%20spend%20more%20and%20provide%20the%20support%20required%20for%20the%20artisans%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20clarifies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrithika%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20sustainable%20architecture%20extends%20beyond%20just%20the%20materials%20she%20uses%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20deeply%20ingrained%20in%20her%20ethical%20approach%20to%20land%20itself.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20get%20me%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20which%20is%20on%20a%20wetland%2C%20I%20will%20not%20take%20it%20up%20as%20a%20project%20because%20it%20is%20going%20to%20create%20issues%20for%20the%20building%20in%20terms%20of%20water%20source%2C%20decomposing%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20asserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20use%20only%20what%20suits%20the%20local%20soil%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrithika%E2%80%99s%20design%20process%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20understanding%20the%20local%20context.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20go%20to%20the%20site%2C%20stay%20there%20for%20a%20week%20at%20least%2C%20understand%20the%20soil%2C%20vegetation%2C%20and%20water%20table%2C%20dig%20up%20the%20soil%2C%20and%20do%20a%20soil%20test%20with%20a%20geotechnical%20engineer%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20prioritises%20hand-dug%20wells%20over%20bore%20wells%20to%20tap%20into%20the%20upper%20aquifer%2C%20which%20is%20a%20layer%20of%20water-holding%20rock%20or%20soil%20that%20is%20closer%20to%20the%20ground%20surface%20and%20can%20store%20and%20provide%20water.%20She%20believes%20that%20documenting%20traditional%20architecture%20in%20surrounding%20villages%20(around%2070%20villages%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu)%20is%20crucial%20for%20understanding%20local%20building%20practices%2C%20material%20proportions%2C%20and%20artisan%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20team%20worked%20closely%20with%20us%20and%20really%20valued%20our%20input%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Krishna.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20through%20six%20or%20seven%20design%20iterations%20before%20finalising%20the%20plan.%E2%80%9D%20The%20construction%20took%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20to%20complete%2C%20with%20some%20delays%20due%20to%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDH0QvW2SErP%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDH0QvW2SErP%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa