ificantly%20lower%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Mohit%2C%20whose%20method%20will%20reduce%20the%20expense%20by%20125%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrash%20%E2%80%94%20even%20a%20problem%20in%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Snehadeep%20and%20Mohit%20are%20deeply%20conscious%20of%20another%20looming%20crisis%3A%20space%20debris.%20%E2%80%9CAryabhata%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20satellite%2C%20launched%20in%201975%2C%20is%20now%20space%20junk.%20No%20one%20even%20knows%20where%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Snehadeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Nebula%E2%80%99s%20CubeSats%20can%20be%20designed%20with%20an%20end-of-life%20plan.%20%E2%80%9CUsing%20solar%20sails%20%E2%80%94%20thin%2C%20reflective%20surfaces%20that%20harness%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20photon%20energy%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20deorbit%20after%20completing%20their%20mission.%20Instead%20of%20cluttering%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20orbit%2C%20the%20CubeSats%20would%20glide%20back%20into%20the%20atmosphere%20and%20disintegrate%20safely%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Mohit%2C%20whose%20idea%20was%20to%20address%20space%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20it%20is%20near%20the%20geo-signal%20orbit%2C%20then%20it%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F413019%2Fisro-yuvika-2025-class-9-students-apply-free-space-programme%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeasier%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20Earth%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20have%20a%20GNSS%20system%20for%20tracking%20and%20a%20TLE%20address%2C%20which%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20MAC%20address%20and%20IP%20address%20on%20our%20phones%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Snehadeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20solar%20sail%20will%20drag%20down%20the%20satellite%20to%20the%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20atmosphere%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20somewhere%20in%20our%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20trajectory.%20We%E2%80%99ll%20find%20the%20geolocation%20of%20it%20and%20retrieve%20it.%20We%20will%20not%20be%20making%20any%20debris%20in%20space%20because%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20add%20any%20more%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Mohit%2C%20all%20of%20which%20can%20be%20monitored%20via%20an%20app%20that%20is%20being%20worked%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20dual-purpose%20innovation%20%E2%80%94%20scientific%20exploration%20without%20environmental%20harm%20%E2%80%94%20is%20core%20to%20Nebula%20Space%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%20ethos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20galaxy%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20years%20of%20intense%20theoretical%20and%20structural%20research%2C%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20prototype%20is%20ready%20on%20paper.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20see%20if%20our%20theoretical%20part%20works%2C%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20making%20this%20effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Snehadeep.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20practicality%20is%20an%20issue%2C%20then%20we%20need%20to%20start%20the%20theory%20from%20scratch%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COurs%20is%20verified%20and%20fact-checked%20by%20scientists%2C%20but%20making%20the%20final%20product%20is%20a%20big%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Snehadeep.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20put%20it%20into%20context%2C%20right%20now%2C%20people%20are%20venturing%20into%206G%20and%20researching%20it%2C%20but%20how%20to%20include%206G%20in%20individual%20phones%20is%20a%20huge%20challenge%2C%20which%20requires%20frequent%20testing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20of%20four%20has%20submitted%20their%20research%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffirst-space-tourist-from-india-gopi-thotakura-shorts-spacetourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20international%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20their%20paper%20was%20accepted%20at%20the%20International%20Astronautical%20Congress%202024%20in%20Milan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20milestones%20for%20any%20emerging%20space%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22illustration%20of%20the%20satellite.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444292%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhile%20the%20theory%20is%20tested%2C%20Nebula%20Space%20Organization%20is%20hopeful%20to%20launch%20the%20satellite%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20big%20hurdle%20ahead%3A%20funding.%20Without%20seed%20investment%2C%20they%20cannot%20move%20to%20full-scale%20production%20and%20testing.%20They%20are%20currently%20in%20talks%20with%20venture%20capitalists%20and%20angel%20investors%20whom%20they%20met%20at%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20mission%20is%20simple%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mohit.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20space%20research%20affordable%20and%20available%20for%20students%20and%20developing%20countries.%E2%80%9D%20With%20India%E2%80%99s%20space%20economy%20projected%20to%20grow%20from%20%248.4%20billion%20in%202024%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Feconomy%2Feconomic-survey-2024-indian-space-sector-sees-increase-in-private-participation-300-indian-entities-file-applications%3F%5C%22%3E%2413%20billion%20by%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20country%20is%20fast%20emerging%20as%20a%20global%20space%20hub.%20Government%20reforms%20and%20increased%20private%20sector%20participation%20have%20further%20accelerated%20this%20momentum%2C%20making%20space%20innovation%20more%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20platform-in-the-making%20promises%20to%20provide%20free%20real-time%20space%20data%20to%20students%20and%20colleges%20globally%2C%20using%20just%20their%20educational%20IDs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vision%20is%20ambitious%20but%20grounded.%20If%20they%20can%20successfully%20detect%20gamma%20rays%20with%20their%20CubeSat%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feat%20no%20Indian%20entity%20has%20achieved%20%E2%80%94%20they%20plan%20to%20expand%20into%20planetary%20imaging%20CubeSats%20and%20interplanetary%20missions%2C%20offering%20affordable%2C%20sustainable%20satellite%20technology%20to%20governments%20and%20private%20players%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20Government%20or%20an%20organisation%20has%20a%20Rs%2010%20million%20budget%20for%20100%20satellites%2C%20that%20will%20be%20a%20boost%20for%20them.%20If%20you%20compare%20the%20cost%20of%20NASA%2C%20which%20is%20500%20million%20dollars%20per%20year%2C%20this%20is%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20Snehadeep%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20mentors%20who%20are%20well-versed%20in%20both%20Physics%20and%20engineering%20to%20guide%20us%20long-term.%20And%20the%20best%20mentors%20are%20from%20ISRO%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Snehadeep%2C%20highlighting%20the%20potential%20for%20India%20to%20succeed%20in%20the%20space%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20see%20space%20as%20the%20final%20frontier%20re